content: sirkitree: Created 17 issues covering feature requests, bug reports, and documentation needs, while merging 6 PRs that added documentation (#46, #62), improved user experience (#42), and maintained dependencies (#147). Made significant code cleanup with PR #67 removing 89 lines of unused code related to sqlite_vss, and contributed actively to discussions with 21 issue comments and 12 PR comments. Activity was sporadic, concentrated on just 4 days this month, with contributions primarily focused on configuration files (65%) and documentation (17%).
